Madɣis u Maziɣ u kenɛan , id-yesɛan Zaḥik 

Akken id-yenna Ben xeldun belli Madɣis d amaraw n Ḍriṣ ( Ǧalut amezzwaru ) ɣef waya qqaren yimaziɣen i unembaḍ-nsen Ǧalut neɣ agellid 

== Amezruy ==
madɣis d amaraw n yiderman imaziɣen ur nuriw id-yesɛa mmi-s zaḥik . Amussnaw n umezruy uday Yusifiyus yenna-d belli imceyyeɛ Yebrahim iceyyeɛ arraw-ines ɣer temnaḍin i ybeɛden ɣef Falesṭin /Israyel , imiren id-unagen ɣer tefriqt n ugafa , ɣef way-a nettaf agdud n tefriqt ttẓallan am udayen  
